text.tspan: Prevalence of anxiety disorders by age, World
Share of population within each age category suffering from an anxiety disorder. This is measured across both sexes.
Figures attempt to provide a true estimate (going beyond reported diagnosis) of anxiety disorder prevalence based on
medical, epidemiological data, surveys and meta-regression modelling.
Source: IHME, Global Burden of Disease
